words.ex: He yanked the door open before anyone could stop him.
The small dog yapped excitedly at the visitors.
She yearned for a chance to travel the world.
He had to yell to be heard over the noise.
The two regions were yoked together under one administration.
A small cottage stood yonder across the field.
The cat yowled loudly when it wanted attention.
Despite his age, he maintained a youthful energy.
